# {{ project_name }}

SvelteKit + TypeScript project scaffolded with [creo](https://github.com/creo-cli/creo).
Runs on port `{{ app_port }}` with hot reload.

## Setup

```bash
cp .env.example .env
creo start {{ project_name }}
```

Then open <http://localhost:{{ app_port }}>.

## Useful commands

```bash
creo logs  {{ project_name }}
creo shell {{ project_name }}
creo run   {{ project_name }} npm run check
creo stop  {{ project_name }}
```

